{"tid":180351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雷雨料未來兩三小時影響本港    氣溫將驟降8℃","createTime":"2017-03-31T01:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T15:47:41.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"34ea45681b22456c2befa9b91f7e11b825b81d1c","tid":180351,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490909268_a90d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490909268_a90d.jpg&h=6eea8d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【09:15更新】現時氣溫23℃，相對濕度百分之92<br />\n【08:45更新】雷暴警告現正生效<br />\n【08:15更新】天文台表示，與冷鋒相關的雷雨帶正從廣東內陸靠近，並會在未來兩三小時影響本港，市民應提高警惕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潮濕的偏東氣流正影響廣東沿岸。本港今早有霧，港內的能見度降至1,000米以下。此外 ，位於廣東北部的一道冷鋒正為該區帶來雷雨，預料該冷鋒會在今日日間橫過沿岸地區 。<br />\n本港今日大致多雲，有幾陣雨，初時有霧。吹和緩東至東南風。日間轉吹清勁北風，雨勢漸轉頻密及有狂風雷暴。氣溫由今日最高約23℃顯著下降至今晚約16℃，而明晨更會低至15℃。"},{"pid":"21382d7d11750557c757ea9f841dbed2addd910a","tid":180351,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:22:36.000Z","msg":"唔係掛，又凍返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c422fc98625e17c8e858262ef847a19303aa6166","tid":180351,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"天文台對唔對得住全球暖化撚？"},{"pid":"e1c8b517bc8beff1ea80fc95197c11d82a4b2d47","tid":180351,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:27:51.000Z","msg":"尖咀好大雨...."},{"pid":"ca1c601bf3bc0959916c518671d12b0e4ede3c7d","tid":180351,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"含得撚 無著外套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffb83460e7d861533c35d3d50a51be0574b74cb","tid":180351,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:29:17.000Z","msg":"好爽，安坐家中聽雨聲"},{"pid":"0a2e1aebd3671b